  "title": "Accounts Assistant",
  "description": "<h3>Job Highlights</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>5 working days per week</li>\n  <li>Provide transport bus in the morning (working day)</li>\n  <li>Excellent potential for advancement.</li>\n</ul>\n<h5><br></h5>\n<h3>Job Description</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Coordinate with external account party;</li>\n  <li>Prepare payments (Cheque, GIRO, TT, FAST &amp; Pay Now);</li>\n  <li>Prepare bank reconciliation and update bank transaction daily;</li>\n  <li>Perform all assigned duties and tasks within scheduled time.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<h3>Requirements</h3>\n<p>¨ Min 1 year experience in handling accounts;</p>\n<p>¨ Knowledge of accounting software, preferably with SAP experience;</p>\n<p>¨ Possess initiative, responsible and able to work independently;</p>\n<p>¨ Good team player.</p>",
